snippet.title: Winterfall - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Winterfall is an open-world RPG set in the awe-inspiring ancient wilds of Anor, the Old Kingdom. Uncover lost knowledge, defend your sanctuary and build a lasting legacy. Coming to PC first. When? TBA



Thank you to all our backers over time and more recently on Patreon.


Join us on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/winterfallgame
Join us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/winterfallgame
Join us on Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/willyouovercome
Join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/ERANgnbSeV
